FUZIX for the N8 Retrobrew Home Computer

Supported
---------
Z180 @18.432MHz with 0x40 I/O base
1MB RAM
TMS 9918A VDP
SD card via CSIO
PPI based IDE
PPI based keyboard
PPI based Mouse
RTC

In Progress
-----------

